-- Insert "Satu Hari di Bali" story
  '["Pagi-pagi banget di Canggu. Vlad baru aja bangun. Dia buka jendelanya dan langsung ngerasa... aduh. Panas banget hari ini! Belum apa-apa udah keringetan.","Dia mandi dulu, terus ganti baju. Celana pendek aja — gak usah ribet. Tapi pas dia lihat keluar jendela lagi... Hmm, kayaknya hujan nih. Kalau hujan gimana ya? Ah, ya udah deh — walaupun hujan, tetap pergi.","Dia ambil tasnya, cari kunci motor, cari HP... Kunci di mana sih? HP-mu mana? Ah, nih. Oke deh. Yuk pergi.","Vlad jalan kaki ke tempat sewa motor di sebelah. Orangnya udah buka. Selamat pagi! Mau ke mana hari ini? Aku mau pergi ke air terjun deket Ubud. Nyewa motor bisa? Bisa dong. Yang mana yang kamu suka? Ada dua nih.","Yang pertama kecil — lebih murah. Yang kedua bagus banget, tapi... Harganya berapa yang kedua? Tujuh puluh lima ribu sehari. Wah, terlalu mahal. Temen aku bilang di sini murah loh. Ya emang gitu, yang bagus emang mahal. Tapi yang pertama cuma empat puluh ribu. Oke, yang pertama aja deh.","Siap bos! Tapi isi bensin dulu ya, hampir kosong nih. Hati-hati di jalan. Aman kok, tenang aja. Kapan balik? Nanti malam. Makasih ya! Sama-sama!","Vlad naik motor ke arah Ubud. Tapi ternyata... jalannya macet banget. Aduh, aku benci macet. Bikin capek banget. Setengah jam kemudian, dia masih di jalan. Perutnya mulai bunyi.","Laper nih... haus banget juga. Eh, ada warung di sana. Makan di warung aja deh. Vlad berhenti dan parkir motornya di pinggir jalan. Warungnya kecil tapi bersih banget.","Permisi! Eh, masuk aja! Duduk di sini. Mau minum apa dulu? Mau air putih aja, haus banget soalnya. Mau nasi atau mie? Nasi goreng satu ya. Pedas? Dikit aja. Oke, tunggu sebentar ya.","Vlad nunggu sambil lihat pemandangan di luar. Sawah hijau, langit biru. Tempatnya enak ya. Desa yang tenang. Beda banget sama Canggu yang rame.","Makanannya datang. Vlad langsung coba. Ya ampun — enak banget makanannya! Asli enak banget. Paling enak sih ini. Haha, makasih ya! Mau lagi?","Udah cukup, perut udah penuh. Eh, siapa yang masak? Ibu sendiri? Iya, aku sendiri. Setiap hari masak dari pagi. Berapa harganya, bu? Dua puluh ribu aja. Masa sih? Murah banget! Di Canggu bisa seratus ribu buat nasi goreng kayak gini. Haha, emang gitu. Di sini murah.","Bu, foto bareng yuk! Buat kenang-kenangan. Oke deh! Senyum dong! Mereka foto bareng di depan warung. Vlad seneng banget. Terima kasih banyak ya bu. Makanannya paling enak. Sama-sama. Hati-hati ya di jalan!","Vlad lanjut naik motor ke air terjun. Sekitar jam tiga dia sampe. Tapi... banyak banget orangnya. Astaga, panjang banget antriannya. Ada loket tiket di depan. Beli tiket dulu ya. Sepuluh ribu satu orang. Satu aja. Gampang.","Vlad jalan turun ke bawah. Jalannya basah kena hujan tadi, jadi agak licin. Aduh, basah banget. Agak takut juga sih, tapi... Terus dia lihat air terjunnya. Lihat itu! Ya ampun — keren banget! Cantik banget. Foto yuk, foto yuk.","Orang di sebelahnya denger Vlad ngomong sendiri, terus dia ketawa. Haha, sering ke sini? Atau baru pertama kali? Baru datang hari ini. Tapi udah tinggal di Bali udah lama banget. Oh ya? Tinggal di mana? Di Canggu. Ah, deket kok dari sini. Kerja di mana?","Aku bikin aplikasi. Kerja sendiri dari laptop. Wah, keren banget! Eh, mau renang gak? Airnya segar loh. Hmm... dingin banget gak? Ya dingin sih, tapi coba deh. Enak kok! Oke deh, yuk!","Mereka renang bareng di bawah air terjun. Segar banget! Seru banget ini. Pengalaman seru deh.","Sore nanti, matahari udah mulai turun. Vlad capek tapi seneng. Capek banget sih, tapi worth it. Ya udah, aku pulang dulu ya. Oke! Sampai jumpa besok mungkin! Haha, mungkin! Dadah!","Vlad naik motor balik ke Canggu. Matahari terik, anginnya kencang. Dia ngerasa capek tapi seneng banget. Akhirnya dia sampe di rumah.","Akhirnya selesai! Badan capek, kaki sakit, tapi hari ini seru banget. Besok mau ke mana lagi ya? Tapi sekarang... Aku mau tidur. Selamat malam."]'::jsonb,
  '["Early morning in Canggu. Vlad just woke up. He opened the window and immediately felt... ugh. So hot today! He was already sweating before doing anything.","He showered first, then changed clothes. Just shorts — no need to overthink it. But when he looked out the window again... Hmm, looks like rain. What if it rains? Ah, whatever — even if it rains, still going.","He grabbed his bag, looked for the motorbike key, looked for his phone... Where is the key? Where is your phone? Ah, here. Okay then. Let''s go.","Vlad walked to the motorbike rental place next door. The guy was already open. Good morning! Where are you going today? I want to go to a waterfall near Ubud. Can I rent a motorbike? Of course. Which one do you like? There are two.","The first one is small — cheaper. The second one is really nice, but... How much is the second one? Seventy-five thousand a day. Wow, too expensive. My friend said this place is cheap. Yeah well, the nice ones are expensive. But the first one is only forty thousand. Okay, the first one then.","Ready boss! But fill up the gas first, it''s almost empty. Be careful on the road. I''ll be fine, don''t worry. When are you coming back? Tonight. Thanks! You''re welcome!","Vlad rode the motorbike toward Ubud. But it turned out... the traffic was really bad. Ugh, I hate traffic. So tiring. Half an hour later, he was still on the road. His stomach started rumbling.","So hungry... really thirsty too. Hey, there''s a warung over there. Let''s just eat at the warung. Vlad stopped and parked his motorbike on the side of the road. The warung was small but really clean.","Excuse me! Hey, come on in! Sit here. What do you want to drink first? Just water, I''m really thirsty. Rice or noodles? One fried rice please. Spicy? Just a little. Okay, wait a moment.","Vlad waited while looking at the view outside. Green rice fields, blue sky. Nice place. A quiet village. So different from busy Canggu.","The food arrived. Vlad tried it right away. Oh my — the food is so good! Genuinely delicious. The best actually. Haha, thank you! Want more?","That''s enough, stomach is full. Hey, who cooked this? You yourself? Yes, me. I cook every day from morning. How much is it, ma''am? Just twenty thousand. Really? So cheap! In Canggu it could be a hundred thousand for fried rice like this. Haha, that''s how it is. It''s cheap here.","Ma''am, let''s take a photo together! As a memory. Okay! Smile! They took a photo together in front of the warung. Vlad was really happy. Thank you so much ma''am. The food was the best. You''re welcome. Be careful on the road!","Vlad continued riding to the waterfall. Around three o''clock he arrived. But... there were so many people. Wow, the line is so long. There''s a ticket booth in front. Buy a ticket first. Ten thousand per person. Just one. Easy.","Vlad walked down. The path was wet from the rain earlier, so it was a bit slippery. Ugh, so wet. A bit scary too, but... Then he saw the waterfall. Look at that! Oh my — so cool! So beautiful. Let''s take photos, let''s take photos.","The person next to him heard Vlad talking to himself, and laughed. Haha, do you come here often? Or is this your first time? Just arrived today. But I''ve been living in Bali for a really long time. Oh really? Where do you live? In Canggu. Ah, that''s close from here. Where do you work?","I make apps. I work by myself from a laptop. Wow, that''s so cool! Hey, want to swim? The water is refreshing. Hmm... is it really cold? Yeah it''s cold, but try it. It''s nice! Okay, let''s go!","They swam together under the waterfall. So refreshing! So fun. What a great experience.","Later in the afternoon, the sun started going down. Vlad was tired but happy. So tired, but worth it. Alright, I''m heading home. Okay! See you tomorrow maybe! Haha, maybe! Bye!","Vlad rode the motorbike back to Canggu. The sun was blazing, the wind was strong. He felt tired but really happy. Finally he arrived home.","Finally done! Body tired, legs sore, but today was so fun. Where should I go tomorrow? But for now... I want to sleep. Good night."]'::jsonb,
  'd3d205dd-98df-481d-bf3f-b4d11b3981f1');

